KMB,UPDATE 1-Venezuela says taking over halted Kimberly-Clark plant CARACAS, July 11 Venezuela's socialist government said on Monday it was taking over and re-activating a plant that U.S. personal care products maker Kimberly-Clark Corp  halted due to the nation's economic crisis. 
KMI,Valero buys remaining stake in Parkway PipelineUPDATE 1-Valero buys out partner in Louisiana-Mississippi pipeline July 12 Valero Energy Corp said on Tuesday it bought Kinder Morgan Inc's 50 percent stake in Parkway Pipeline LLC, previously a joint venture between the two companies.  UPDATE 1-Valero buys out partner in Louisiana-Mississippi pipeline July 12 Valero Energy Corp said on Tuesday it bought Kinder Morgan Inc's 50 percent stake in Parkway Pipeline LLC, previously a joint venture between the two companies.
